<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.1.9">
<l>paṭimaṉṉu palkalaṉ paṟṟō ṭaṟuttaim pulaṉveṉṟu</l>
<l>ceṭimaṉṉu kāyamceṟ ṟārkaḷu māṅkava ṉaiyillār</l>
<l>kuṭimaṉṉu miṉcuvarkka meytiyu mīḷvarkaṇ mīḷvillai</l>
<l>koṭimaṉṉu puḷḷuṭai yaṇṇal kaḻalkaḷ kuṟukumiṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Also those who vanquish five senses, cutting off the many vessels in which they remain on earth along with attachment,</l>
<l>[and] subdue [their] bodies in which sin remains, being those who are there without him,</l>
<l>even if they reach flashing heaven where intoxication lasts, for them returning there is no return.</l>
<l>Approach the ankletted [feet] of the majesty with a bird that stays on [his] banner.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
